import os
import random
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
from PIL import Image

# YOUR ACTUAL FOLDER LOCATION
BASE_DIR = "../data/tomatoleaf/tomato"

TRAIN_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, "train")
VAL_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, "val")

print("TRAIN FOLDER:", TRAIN_DIR)
print("VAL FOLDER:", VAL_DIR)

In[7]:
plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))

for i, cls in enumerate(classes[:9]):
    cls_path = os.path.join(TRAIN_DIR, cls)
    file = random.choice(os.listdir(cls_path))
    img = Image.open(os.path.join(cls_path, file))
    
    plt.subplot(3,3,i+1)
    plt.imshow(img)
    plt.title(cls)
    plt.axis("off")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
In[8]:
corrupt_files = []

for cls in classes:
    cls_path = os.path.join(TRAIN_DIR, cls)
    for fname in os.listdir(cls_path):
        try:
            Image.open(os.path.join(cls_path, fname))
        except:
            corrupt_files.append((cls, fname))

corrupt_files[:10], len(corrupt_files)
